Collectives require the following:

* Collective name
* Collective handle that determines the URL of the collective (i.e. https://app.harmonic.local/collectives/collective-handle-example)
* Collective description (optional) that appears on the collective homepage
* Timezone, which determines when daily cycles begin and end
* Tempo ("daily", "weekly", or "monthly"), which determines how frequently other collective members should check in
* Synchronization mode ("improv" or "orchestra"), which determines default permissions for new members
  * "improv" (default) is for groups with no formal leadership roles
  * "orchestra" is for groups with formal leadership roles

